{"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\"/><title>Create New Campaign - Marketing Launcher</title><meta name=\"next-head-count\" content=\"3\"/><script async=\"\" src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-13DDMQLQFZ\"></script><script>\n                    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n                    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n                    gtag('js', new Date());\n                    gtag('config', 'G-13DDMQLQFZ', {\n                      page_path: window.location.pathname,\n                    });\n                  </script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/css/3b0c939fc99db33f.css\" as=\"style\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/3b0c939fc99db33f.css\" data-n-g=\"\"/><noscript data-n-css=\"\"></noscript><script defer=\"\" nomodule=\"\" src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-a146a8ef8f1e9d05.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/framework-e08ca35bb8c7d6c2.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-ecf9fdf2fdcbcf0c.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/pages/_app-a4b465d0d03c3032.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/7703-0be1e1ca03344042.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/pages/marketing/launcher/new-9accd60006ae3a1f.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/A8ZS1-JPDIjUeTFM33ndo/_buildManifest.js\" defer=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/A8ZS1-JPDIjUeTFM33ndo/_ssgManifest.js\" defer=\"\"></script></head><body><div id=\"__next\"><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-blue-50\"><header class=\"bg-white shadow\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-6\"><button class=\"text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-900 font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\">← Back</button><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Create New Campaign</h1><p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-2\">Design and configure your email campaign</p></div></header><main class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12\"><div class=\"bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 text-blue-700 px-6 py-4 rounded-lg mb-6\"><p class=\"font-semibold\">🔄 Initializing authentication...</p><p class=\"text-sm mt-1\">Please wait while we verify your session.</p></div><form class=\"bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 space-y-8\"><fieldset class=\"space-y-6\"><legend class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Campaign Information</legend><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">Campaign Name *</label><input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"e.g., Q1 Product Launch - Jobseekers\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent\" required=\"\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1\">Internal name to track this campaign</p></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">Description</label><textarea name=\"description\" placeholder=\"Optional notes about this campaign&#x27;s goals and audience\" rows=\"3\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent\"></textarea></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"space-y-6\"><legend class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Email Content</legend><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">Email Subject *</label><input type=\"text\" name=\"email_subject\" placeholder=\"e.g., Introducing Take The Reigns - Job Hiring Platform\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent\" required=\"\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1\">Recipients will see this in their inbox</p></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">Reply-To Email Address</label><input type=\"email\" name=\"reply_to_email\" placeholder=\"e.g., hello@yourcompany.com\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1\">When recipients hit Reply, their response goes here. Defaults to Info@take-the-reins.ai if left blank.</p></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">CSV Email Parameters</label><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">When uploading a CSV file, you can include these columns to personalize emails:</p><div class=\"bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6 overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-300\"><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2 font-semibold text-gray-700\">Parameter</th><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2 font-semibold text-gray-700\">Type</th><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2 font-semibold text-gray-700\">Required</th><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2 font-semibold text-gray-700\">Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-mono text-purple-600\">email</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\">String</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\"><span class=\"bg-red-100 text-red-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">Yes</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-gray-600\">Must be a valid email address</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-mono text-purple-600\">name</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\">String</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\"><span class=\"bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">Optional</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-gray-600\">Full name - splits into first/last</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-mono text-purple-600\">first_name</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\">String</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\"><span class=\"bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">Optional</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-gray-600\">First name only (auto-extracted from name)</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-mono text-purple-600\">last_name</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\">String</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\"><span class=\"bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">Optional</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-gray-600\">Last name only (auto-extracted from name)</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-gray-200\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-mono text-purple-600\">target_role</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\">String</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\"><span class=\"bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">Optional</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-gray-600\">Job role/title of recipient</td></tr><tr><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-mono text-purple-600\">target_industry</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\">String</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2\"><span class=\"bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">Optional</span></td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-gray-600\">Industry of the recipient</td></tr></tbody></table></div><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\"><strong>Example CSV:</strong> <span class=\"font-mono text-sm bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded\">email,name,target_role</span></p></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">Email Body (HTML) *</label><textarea name=\"email_body_html\" placeholder=\"Paste your HTML email template here. Use [RECIPIENT_NAME] for personalization.\" rows=\"8\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent font-mono text-sm\" required=\"\"></textarea><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1\">Supports HTML. Use [RECIPIENT_NAME] to personalize messages. Include tracking pixel at the end.</p></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"space-y-6\"><legend class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Campaign Settings</legend><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">Target Audience</label><select name=\"target_audience_segment\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent\"><option value=\"custom\" selected=\"\">Custom List</option><option value=\"unemployed\">Unemployed / Job Seekers</option><option value=\"hired\">Recently Hired</option></select></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">List Source</label><select name=\"list_source\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent\"><option value=\"imported\" selected=\"\">Imported CSV</option><option value=\"internal\">Internal Subscribers</option><option value=\"hunter\">Hunter.io</option><option value=\"linkedin\">LinkedIn</option></select></div></div><div><label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2\">UTM Campaign Tag</label><input type=\"text\" name=\"utm_campaign\" placeholder=\"Auto-filled with campaign name if left blank\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-purple-500 focus:border-transparent\" value=\"\"/><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1\">Used for Google Analytics tracking</p></div></fieldset><fieldset class=\"space-y-4\"><legend class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Upload Recipients (CSV)</legend><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\">Upload your recipient list now, or you can do it after creating the campaign.</p><div class=\"bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-5 space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border border-blue-100\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1\">CSV Format:</p><pre class=\"bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-xs overflow-x-auto\">email,name\njohn@example.com,John Doe\njane@example.com,Jane Smith</pre><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">Header row required. Name and other columns are optional.</p></div><div><label class=\"block\"><span class=\"sr-only\">Choose CSV file</span><input type=\"file\" accept=\".csv\" class=\"block w-full text-sm text-gray-500 file:mr-4 file:py-2 file:px-4 file:rounded-lg file:border-0 file:text-sm file:font-semibold file:bg-blue-50 file:text-blue-700 hover:file:bg-blue-100 disabled:opacity-50\"/></label></div></div></fieldset><div class=\"flex gap-4 pt-6\"><button type=\"submit\" disabled=\"\" class=\"flex-1 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 disabled:bg-gray-400 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition\">Loading...</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"px-6 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition\">Cancel</button></div></form></main></div></div><script id=\"__NEXT_DATA__\" type=\"application/json\">{\"props\":{\"pageProps\":{}},\"page\":\"/marketing/launcher/new\",\"query\":{},\"buildId\":\"A8ZS1-JPDIjUeTFM33ndo\",\"nextExport\":true,\"autoExport\":true,\"isFallback\":false,\"scriptLoader\":[]}</script></body></html>","isFullyStaticPage":true}